steps.instructions: Head east on City Hall Park Path toward Centre St
City Hall Park Path turns slightly left and becomes Brooklyn Bridge Promenade
Turn left to stay on Brooklyn Bridge Promenade

Turn left at Pearl St
Walk your bicycle

Turn left onto 3rd Ave
Pass by Duane Reade (on the right)
Turn left after Duane Reade (on the left)
Williamsburg Bridge Path turns slightly left and becomes Williamsburg Bridge Bicycle Path
Turn left to stay on Williamsburg Bridge Bicycle Path

Turn right at N Henry St
Walk your bicycle

Slight left toward Monitor St
Walk your bicycle

Turn left onto Meeker Ave
Pass by McDonald's (on the right)
Morgan Ave turns slightly left and becomes Wilson Ave
Slight right after Day & Night Deli (on the right)

Turn right onto Monroe St
Pass by Key Food Supermarkets (on the right in 1.1 mi)

Turn right onto St Marks Ave
Walk your bicycle
Turn right to stay on Brooklyn Bridge Park Greenway
Turn left to stay on Brooklyn Bridge Park Greenway

Turn left onto Chambers St
Parts of this road may be closed at certain times or days

Turn left onto City Hall Park Path
Destination will be on the right
